<item>
            <title>[LU-1072] grouplock glimpse callback on mdt do multiple free</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1072</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when mdt takes a grouplock (mdd_file_lock()) it allocates an ma and free it in the glimpse grouplock callback.&lt;br/&gt;
the cb is called for each stripe so the ma is freed multiple time&lt;br/&gt;
the proposed patch (gerrit will follow) is to use a global ma structure allocated out of the lock/unlock sequence&lt;/p&gt;</description>
